Who We Are

















My name is Lori Ors and I eat, sleep and breathe illustration and graphic design. Offering a wide array of creative services for people in need of creative solutions. Some clients include: Atlanta Magazine, Spanx, Inc., TAPS Paramagazine of Syfy's Ghost Hunters, DIRECTV, ADT, Trident Marketing and many more.Education: BFA in Visual Communications - Graphic DesignSkills: Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator, Adobe InDesign, Quark, Adobe Acrobat Pro, Microsoft Word, Pen & Ink, Acrylic











